suggestions.title: Support latest dependencies.
suggestions.description: The version constraint in `pubspec.yaml` does not support the latest published versions for 2 dependencies (`analyzer`, `html`).

suggestions.title: The package description is too short.
suggestions.description: Add more detail to the `description` field of `pubspec.yaml`. Use 60 to 180 characters to describe the package, what it does, and its target use case.

suggestions.title: Maintain an example.
suggestions.description:
Create a short demo in the `example/` directory to show how to use this package.

Common filename patterns include `main.dart`, `example.dart`, and `dartdoc.dart`. Packages with multiple examples should provide `example/README.md`.

For more information see the [pub package layout conventions](https://www.dartlang.org/tools/pub/package-layout#examples).
